  The new comer Samsung Galaxy S9 is set to rock the mobile market in South Africa as it promises to be one of the best smartphones to be designed. The Samsung Galaxy S9 is already trending on Twitter in South Africa as it recorded 9000 tweets on the third week of March 2018. This cute S9 is expected to arrive in South Africa before the end March and many retailers cannot wait to have it on their shelves. This smartphone is priced as follows in South Africa The Samsung Galaxy S9 – R15,499 Samsung Galaxy S9+ – R17,999 The Samsung Galaxy S9 and S9+ are Samsung’s latest Android flagship smartphones, and pack an array of impressive features.